# ECG Monitoring System Overview

This project implements a complete cardiac monitoring system (ECG) using an AD8232 sensor connected to a Raspberry Pi, with web servers for configuration, acquisition, visualization, and diagnosis.

## Project Structure

- [docker-compose.yml](mdc:docker-compose.yml): Docker configuration for the whole system
- [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile): Web server container configuration
- [database/init.sql](mdc:database/init.sql): Database schema initialization

### Web Application Structure:
- [web/public/index.php](mdc:web/public/index.php): Main entry point for the web application
- [web/includes/functions.php](mdc:web/includes/functions.php): Common utility functions
- [web/config/database.php](mdc:web/config/database.php): Database connection functions
- [web/config/security.php](mdc:web/config/security.php): Security functions for data protection
